com.toldcalculator.android.tc.controller.helpers

Class BundleConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.toldcalculator.android.tc.controller.helpers.BundleConstants

  • public class BundleConstants
extends Object
    This class contains constants that are used for keys to pass information between fragments using bundles. Probably not the best way to do this but this will do for now.
